        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": ". . .",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—Here it is implied that the language of Scripture concerning Solomon was familiar both to Nehemiah and to these transgressors. It is a remarkable instance of the faithful application of their own chronicles.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
